Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,XFF二次修改以匹配时长1:33:12 蓝光版本
Dialogue: 3,0:00:57.46,0:01:00.62,SimpleLine,,0000,0000,0000,,双重人格
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你坐了我的位置\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You're in my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你坐了我的位置\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You're in my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 对不起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 你啊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我？- 宾客得登记\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Me? - Visitors have to sign in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等下 我在这工作七年了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh wait, I've worked here for seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我每天都能见到你 - 我周末都不上班的…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- I see you every day. - I don't work weekends...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么？- 如果你说…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- I'm sorry? - ...It is therefore impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你每天都见到我是不可能的 证件\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for you to see me every day. I.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好的 我… - 附属证件\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Yeah, I... - Supplementary I.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 可笑的是我没法出示其他证件\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh yeah, the funny thing is I don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们都在我的文件包了 而文件包又被夹在列车门了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's actually in my case, which is in the door of a train.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 太糟糕了 - 你觉得这很好笑吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- It got stuck. - Do you think that's funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 它比任何事都令我烦心\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No. No, it's actually more upsetting than anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生 别拿这来开玩笑\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Don't make a jest of this, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是玩笑\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 嗯… 实际上 我的姓名是西蒙·詹姆斯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, um... Actually my name is Simon James.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你漏写了我的姓\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Uh, you left off the "J" in my last name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 请出示通行证 - 好的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- I need to see your pass. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:04:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打搅了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sorry.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:12.58,0:06:16.83,SimpleLine,,0000,0000,0000,,办公室就像是野外丛林 让上校帮助你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿好你的外套 小子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Put your jacket on, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里可不是妓院\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This isn't a brothel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别偷懒 这可是个矢志的追求\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No shirking! This is the big push!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上校希望你们每个人都有所作为 我也如此\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Plenty to do. The Colonel is counting on each and every one of you, as am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实际上… 帕帕多普洛斯先生 对不起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mr. Papadopoulos, actually... Mr. Papadopoulos, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕帕多普洛斯先生 我做完工作了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mr. Papadopoulos, I've finished up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.03,0:06:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实际上 我还超额完成了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In fact, I completed substantially more than my quota.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我脱外套是因为真的很热\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I took my jacket off only because it's so hot,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:06:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并不是因为我把办公室当妓院\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}not because I mistook the office for a brothel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做得好 主动工作正是我们所需要的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Excellent job. That's the type of initiative we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小子 你在这里工作多久了？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}How long have you been here, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 刚来上班吗？- 是的 已经工作七年了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Just started, eh? - Yes sir, seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要知道 我们如今正在修剪朽木\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You know we've been pruning the dead wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上校不允许再养更多的闲散人员了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Colonel refuses to carry any more passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 其实 我有一些相当出色的想法…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Er, actually, I have some rather exciting ideas
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是关于如何"让报告更有效率"的…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I've been wanting to share with the Colonel about how
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想和上校分享下这方面想法\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we could make our reports more efficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我构想用单元回归分析…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I think by using simple regression analysis
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就可以重新配置整个业务\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we could really reconfigure the entire business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 梅兰妮 我女儿的名字 - 名字真好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- My daughter's name is Melanie. - A nice name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她暑假在这实习\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}She's interning for the holidays.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 梅兰妮 打个招呼吧 - 你好 梅兰妮\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Say hello, Melanie. - Hello, Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里 斯坦利会成为你的导师\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Stanley here is gonna be your mentor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好 什么？- 每天一个小时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Yes. What? - An hour a day,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己决定  她是个好女孩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}at your discretion. She's a good girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 但是却是个数盲 - 好的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- but no head for figures. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你现在可以走了 - 好的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- You can go now. - Right. Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我发现你在这儿做的事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Because if I were to find out how depressing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令我感到压抑和低贱 诸如此类的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and demeaning whatever the fuck it is you do here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能得为你感到抱歉了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I might be forced to feel sorry for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 好的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Right. Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拭目以待\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I look forward to it.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:03.23,0:08:05.29,SimpleLine,,0000,0000,0000,,文件份数
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,复印\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你不打印两份 那才合逻辑\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Why don't you print out two copies? That would make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般人都会这样做的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That would be what a normal person would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 对不起 - 这里不是让你复印一份用的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Sorry. - You can't use this place for one copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.36,0:09:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 昨天你也是这样 - 对不起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- It was the same story yesterday. - Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你经常道歉 - 为此我感到抱歉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- You're always sorry. - Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 汉娜 你能再留一会儿吗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hey, Hannah, can you stay late?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我还有点事 - 好的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- I've gotta get this thing lanced. - Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,复印一份\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 谢谢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:09:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 妈妈 我会去的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yes, mom, I'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我老是加班\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I always work late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.46,0:10:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就要去了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm trying to leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.43,0:10:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我现在还在和你说话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Because I'm talking to you. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.66,0:10:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 再见\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Okay. Yes. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.76,0:10:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要相信我 好的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You can rely on me. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:11:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人力资源…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}People...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最基本的资源\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The ultimate resource.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于某些企业而言 人力资源看起来没什么区别\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yet to some businesses they all look the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但上校知道 他们其实是有区别的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the Colonel knows people are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上校做的是关于"人"的生意 是在用"人"做生意\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Colonel knows business is people and people are business,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.43,0:11:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你有需求 他就能生产\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}making your business his business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为上校熟知"人"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Because the Colonel knows people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且上校明白 你必须…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And the Colonel knows that you demand
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.83,0:11:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用世界上最先进的数据分析系统…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the most powerful data-processing system
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来分析这些"人力资源"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}on the planet to make sense of it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上校会用你业务…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Colonel will show you people
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能理解的方式来向你展现这些\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in a way your business can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.33,0:11:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在上校眼里 这里没有什么…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Because the Colonel knows there's no such thing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是特殊存在的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as special people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何人不过是人而已\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Just people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 哪个是你？- 哪个…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Which one was you? - Which one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道该怎么说\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I don't know how to answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 那个就是我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The one... the one that was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.76,0:11:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个看起来不像你 他的头发是棕色的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He didn't look like you. He had brown hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都有棕色的头发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We both have brown hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我意思是 我… 我们都是同样的人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I mean, I have... I... We're the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.80,0:11:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我永远不会死的… - 我知道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- I'm not gonna die ever... - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:11:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 因此你可以忘掉它 - 好的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- ...so you can forget it. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以闭嘴了吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Will you stop talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打算睡觉了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm trying to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈说你是个奇怪的孩子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Your mother says you're a strange boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么？- 你妈妈说你很奇怪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- I'm sorry? - Your mother says you're a strange boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 谢谢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.76,0:12:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看你的手掌\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Let me see your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 我过得挺好的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, that's okay. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你过得不好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You're not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以和你谈谈吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}May I speak with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以走开下吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Will you excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的账单看来有点不符\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There seems to be a discrepancy in your bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.36,0:12:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 对哦 费用增涨了很多而且…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh yes, well, there was a rather large cost increase
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 没有解释说明 所以我认为… - 调价了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- and no explanation, so I thought... - There's a new price.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 为什么呢？- 服务改善了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- And why is that? - Improvements.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这听起来有点… - 不公平\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- That seems a little... - Unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 对不起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:12:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就只有这些了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's all I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.06,0:13:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不够\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.89,0:17:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不应该那样做\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You shouldn't be doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.86,0:17:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 然后你又做了什么？- 什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- And then what did you do? - Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:18:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后你又做了什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And then what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我报警了 - 嗯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- I called the police. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有别的吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他向我挥手\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He waved at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.36,0:19:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么？- 他跳楼之前和我挥手\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Yeah? - Right before he jumped he waved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.53,0:19:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么挥的？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}How did he wave?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你也向他挥手了吗？- 我想知道他为什么这么做\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Did you wave back? - I wonder why he did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他遗书写下他很寂寞 他应该养一只狗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}His note said he was lonely. He should have got a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者多锻炼 这很重要\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Or exercised more. That's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我该把这写下来吗？- 应该加上括弧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Should I write that down? - Maybe in parenthesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 意思是用大括弧？- 大括弧是什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Does that mean brackets? - What the fuck are brackets?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他很痛苦吗？- 啪嗒就死了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Did he suffer? - Splat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们经常遇到这样的事情吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Do you see this sort of thing often?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天 这就是我们做的 处理自杀\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Every day. That's what we do... suicides.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 单单处理自杀？- 是的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Only suicides? - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 整个城市的？- 我们就只负责这周边\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- For the whole city? - We can barely cover the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道 有趣的是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You know the funny thing is
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.89,0:19:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他再往右边跳一点 他应该能在篷布那落点\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}he would have landed on that awning if he'd just jumped a few feet to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.89,0:19:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看见那吗？他跳下来 然后弹开\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You see that? He would have fallen, bounced off
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后摔在那的某处\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and landed somewhere about there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.36,0:19:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样可能会保住性命\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Probably would have survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.03,0:19:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的是 那样至少残废了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Horribly maimed, of course, but still.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你及时送他到医院 处理脑袋膨胀\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you get 'em to the hospital quick enough to stop the brain swelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有在想着自杀 对吧？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You're not thinking of killing yourself, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.43,0:19:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这是个简单的问题 - 没有\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- It's a simple question. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.66,0:19:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我应该把他记录为"不会"吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Should I put him down as a "no"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:20:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他记录成"可能"吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Put him down as a "maybe."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这干什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那男人在那跳下来的？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The man that jumped?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我看见了 - 怎么跳？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- I saw it. - How?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我住在那栋楼\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I live in that building.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不认识他\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I didn't know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他朝我挥手 - 真奇怪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- He waved at me. - Strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.39,0:20:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天是上校的舞会\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's the Colonel's ball tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去吗？我不知道去不去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Do you think you'll go? I don't know if I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.89,0:20:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是强制性的 每个人都得去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's mandatory. Everyone has to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.39,0:20:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汉娜？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hannah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.33,0:20:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孤独一人真是太糟糕了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's terrible to be alone too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:20:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一杯果汁 我要的是…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I think it was an orange juice. I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:21:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们的服务都是那么差吗？- 是的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Are they normally that rude here? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那你为什么还来？- 我想是我忠贞吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Then why do you come? - I think I'm quite loyal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得交出你的徽章和手枪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You'll have to hand in your holo-badge and blaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.63,0:21:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来拿啊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Come and get 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.73,0:21:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把枪放下 杰克\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Holster your blaster, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.83,0:21:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢这节目\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I like this show.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不介意死去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I don't mind dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.69,0:21:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实际上 我还习惯了这样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In fact, I'm getting quite used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.53,0:21:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按我推测 你只有一条命\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The way I figure it, you only get one life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和他们说的那样…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And like they say...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.09,0:21:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人生没有第二次机会\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's no such thing as second chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克 那不是你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Jack, this isn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.89,0:21:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我他妈的是谁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Then who the hell is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.83,0:21:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在你心里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He's in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.46,0:21:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他真善美\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He's good and right and true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说不认识他 我撒谎了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I was lying when I said I didn't know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳楼那个人 某程度上我认识他\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The man who jumped? I kind of knew him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.89,0:21:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有真正和他见过面 我只瞥见过他\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'd never really met him. I'd more confronted him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:21:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那人跟踪我好一段时间了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He was this person who'd been following me around for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.89,0:22:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去到哪里都能见到他\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and I'd always see him, no matter where I went...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是在办公室 地铁站 公寓里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Like at the office, on the subway, by my apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.93,0:22:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗？在公寓的地下道里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You know, in that little underpass thing by the apartments?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.93,0:22:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就在那 看着我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He'd just be there, watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我在想 "这太奇怪了" 但是 无论怎么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And I thought, "that's strange." But, you know, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.73,0:22:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人看女人 看多了你就会习惯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Men look at women. You get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.09,0:22:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 后来我发现 他就在我生活里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But then I found out that he lived above me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就想 "这太诡异了"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and I thought, "that's really odd."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.36,0:22:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是因为他和我住在同一栋楼 于是到处跟着我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Like, did he follow me around because he lived in the same building as me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.86,0:22:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因而迷恋上我 又或者是他因为迷恋我而搬来这里？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and he got fixated? Or did he get fixated and then move in?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.76,0:22:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样 最后我在想"你知道什么？"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So anyway, eventually I thought, "you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"够了就是够了" 因为这事实上已经够恐怖的了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Enough is enough." Because it was actually getting frightening.
