Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.86,0:32:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你在摸我的耳垂吗？- 是啊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Are you touching my earlobe? - Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.89,0:32:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还小吗？还玩这？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Aren't you like a million years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.33,0:32:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 别为这吵架 - 哈瑞斯 这不妥当\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Don't fight this. - Harris, that's not appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.53,0:32:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不去死？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Why won't you die?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.03,0:32:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该多请你这种青年才俊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We could really use a bright young man like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.86,0:32:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在 我们又有了巨大的推进了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Especially right now, with the big push and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.76,0:32:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得向各位介绍我们的新员工\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'd like to introduce everyone to our newest co-worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.53,0:32:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我敢肯定你会变为年轻的骨干精英的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A bright young man who I'm sure will be an asset.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.96,0:32:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我们的子公司 他在最后一轮裁员也没被开除\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He was the only one not fired in the final cull at our sister office.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.59,0:32:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里甚至连蟑螂都不能存活下来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Even the cockroaches didn't survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.89,0:33:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我要让你开始了 年轻的高手\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, I'll let you get started, young hotshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.69,0:33:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快 你就会接替我的工作\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Soon you'll have my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.33,0:33:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位 请欢迎 詹姆斯·西蒙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Everyone, please welcome James Simon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.53,0:33:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必惊慌 我家的清洁阿姨是位糖尿病患者\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's no need to be alarmed. My cleaning lady's a diabetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.73,0:33:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只需把饼干塞进他的喉咙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We just need to jam a cookie down his throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.03,0:33:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 先生 我没糖尿病\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, no, sir, I'm not diabetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.69,0:33:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 只是吓坏了… - 别担心 小子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- It's just a shock that... - Don't worry, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.69,0:33:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是要取代你 我不是那种假仁假义的人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We're not replacing you. I'm not one of these holier-than-thou types.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.69,0:33:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗑药也能使人健康 但别带来办公室就好了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Drugs can be healthy for a person. Just leave it out of the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.69,0:33:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 我没嗑药 先生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, no, not drugs, sir. No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.99,0:33:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚只是个误会 现在…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Last night was a mistake. And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.79,0:33:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在 这个陌生人 我只是…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now... now this strange man, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.59,0:33:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必细说 我们都经历过那种事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No need for details. It's happened to us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.73,0:33:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝杯水 然后回去工作\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Have a drink of water then get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.86,0:34:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈瑞斯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Harris.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.53,0:34:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈瑞斯 你和新同事说过话了吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Harris, have you spoken to the new employee?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.93,0:34:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 詹姆斯吗？说过了 - 怎样？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- James? Yeah sure, I met him. - And?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.33,0:34:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他挺好的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He seems all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.69,0:34:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你有注意到他有点奇怪吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But did you notice anything strange about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.73,0:34:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我意思是 他有令你想起谁吗？- 没有\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- I mean, did he remind you of anyone? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.83,0:34:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 没想起办公室的某人？- 没有\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- No one at the office? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.73,0:34:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 请…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Okay. Would...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.93,0:34:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请我… 你…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Can I... could you...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.69,0:34:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以过… 你可…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Would... could I please just...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.43,0:34:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以过…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You can...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.79,0:34:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.06,0:34:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.66,0:35:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你觉得他让你想起谁？- 例如 我啊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Who did you have in mind? - Me, for instance.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.66,0:35:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 可能吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh yeah, suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.43,0:35:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只是可能？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You suppose so?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.33,0:35:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 是吧 你看起来很像他\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yeah yeah, you look just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.43,0:35:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是啦 不像吗？- 像 你又不是中国人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Yes, I do, don't I? - Yeah, and you're not even Chinese.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.83,0:35:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这真是太乱了 - 是啊 乱啊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- It's pretty fucked up. - Yes, it is that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.69,0:35:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在 为什么你没注意到？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now now why didn't you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.03,0:35:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 请勿见怪 哥们 但…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, no offense, mate, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.86,0:35:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的不太令人瞩目\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You're pretty unnoticeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.99,0:35:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点像透明人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Bit of a non-person.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.09,0:37:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要吃点什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What'll it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.76,0:37:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要什么？好的 嗯 抱歉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What, do you want to go...? Okay, no, sorry then.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.79,0:37:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要… 可乐和面包圈\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'll just have a... Coke and a bagel.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.06,0:37:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 面包圈卖完了 - 噢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- We're out of bagels. - Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.66,0:37:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 那…嗯…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Right, then, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.83,0:37:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 那 我要…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Right. Then I'll just...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.53,0:37:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 快点 - 好的 抱歉 我要…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Come on. - Right, sorry, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.76,0:37:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要… 我就要一杯可乐就好了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'll just... I can just have the coke then, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.33,0:37:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 可乐一杯 你呢？- 咖啡\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- A coke. And you? - A coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.09,0:37:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 咖啡一杯 - 还有西式炒蛋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- A coffee. - And scrambled eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.79,0:37:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们晚上不卖早餐\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We don't serve breakfast in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.63,0:37:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 为什么不卖？- 因为菜单上明写着的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Why not? - Because it says so on the menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.09,0:37:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那好 你们还有鸡蛋吧？- 有啊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Well, do you still have eggs here? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.89,0:37:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那你们还有煎锅吧？- 有的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- And do you have a frying pan? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.53,0:37:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那帮帮忙 弄个西式炒蛋给我吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Then do me a favor and make me some scrambled eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.79,0:37:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 可以 还有什么吗？- 培根\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Fine. Anything else? - Bacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.86,0:37:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 培根一份 - 还有烤面包\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Bacon. - And toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.49,0:37:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 烤面包一份 - 还有啤酒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- And toast. - And a beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.06,0:37:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有啤酒一瓶 还有别的吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And a beer. Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.76,0:37:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 没了 就这些 - 你确定？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- No, that's it. - Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.03,0:38:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就他妈这些了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Just get me the damn food.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.86,0:38:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么？我很饿 - 不 这…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- What? I'm hungry. - No, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.03,0:38:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 我从来没这要做过\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I don't know, I would have never done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.46,0:38:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你不喜欢鸡蛋？- 不 我意思是 我…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- You don't like eggs? - No, I mean, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.43,0:38:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样和别人说话令我感到很不安\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Don't think I would feel comfortable talking to someone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.69,0:38:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她只是个侍应 她在这就是为了服务我们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}She's a waitress. She's here to serve us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.73,0:38:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不告诉她你真正想要的 她怎么工作呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you don't tell her what you actually want, how can she do her job?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.03,0:38:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我看得出… 她有时候会有点秀逗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, I can see that... She can be a little short sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.76,0:38:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我也觉得 直率无疑也很重要\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and I do think being forthright certainly has its place.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.33,0:38:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是批评你的做法不好什么的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And I'm not, like, criticizing your behavior or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.69,0:38:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的咖啡\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Here is your coffee,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.53,0:38:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啤酒 还有你的早餐\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}your beer and your breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.93,0:38:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可乐卖完了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We're out of coke.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.96,0:38:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你俩的手都好漂亮喔\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You both have very beautiful hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.09,0:38:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请继续\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To be continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.33,0:38:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别走开\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Don't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.36,0:38:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深色头发那个挺开放的 你想要哪个？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The dark-haired one is a dirty dirty thing. Which one do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.66,0:38:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么？- 但我喜欢咖啡色那个 你选吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- I'm sorry? - I prefer the brunette, but either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.43,0:38:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 你两个都要也可以\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's all right, you can have both.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.43,0:39:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 可一不可再啦 - 我要去下洗手间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Never again. - I'm gonna go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.63,0:39:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嘿 看着 瞎眼了？- 对不起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Hey, watch it, will you? - Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.53,0:39:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你他妈的想怎样？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What the fuck are you gonna do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.33,0:39:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我们大概不认识吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hi, I don't think we've talked.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.69,0:39:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以帮我拿下瓶子吗？谢谢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Would you mind holding this for me? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.86,0:39:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得走了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We should leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.59,0:39:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会没女友呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}How come you don't have a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.39,0:39:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不清楚\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.63,0:39:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是同性恋？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You a flamer?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.39,0:39:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我心里总想着一个人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, there's someone I've been thinking about.
