Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.96,1:01:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yeah, I just...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.79,1:01:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你想想 帕帕多普洛斯会相信谁呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now who do you think Papadopoulos is gonna believe?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.93,1:01:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那个他称呼斯坦利的员工呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Some dink he still calls Stanley?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.49,1:01:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抑或是 这个家伙呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Or this guy?
Dialogue: 3,1:01:19.66,1:01:21.06,SimpleLine,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯·西蒙 高级主管
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.52,1:01:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样 我要你公寓的钥匙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So I need the key... To your apartment.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.49,1:01:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要知道 梅兰妮的叫声有点尖\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You see, Melanie is a bit of a screamer
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.56,1:01:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有 我不希望汉娜上来引发另一般景象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and I don't want Hannah coming up and making another scene.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.12,1:01:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们到你那里 事情就变得简单了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It'll just be easier if we use your place.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.89,1:01:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你是想再看看这照片呢 还是你答应呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now do you need to see the photo again or are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.16,1:01:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也会带其他女人上那的 以防你闻到了不同的香味\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'll also be taking other women up there in case you notice different smells.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.96,1:01:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.69,1:01:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是詹姆斯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm James.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.46,1:01:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Get up.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.16,1:02:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Get up.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.09,1:02:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是你想像死蛇一样 死在地上？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Or do you wanna die on the ground, like a snake?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.02,1:02:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在这\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There he is.
Dialogue: 3,1:02:48.89,1:02:50.89,SimpleLine,,0000,0000,0000,,回归分析 作者西蒙·詹姆斯
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.92,1:02:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嘿 你在做什么工作？- 这是私隐\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Hey, what are you working on? - It's private.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.83,1:02:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你不要靠着我的工作台\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Can you please not lean on my work station?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.56,1:03:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我还需要钥匙 - 不行\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- So I need that key again. - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.43,1:03:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 可一不可再 - 好的 我懂了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- That was it. No more. - All right, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.99,1:03:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 帕帕多普洛斯先生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hey, Mr. Papadopoulos.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.56,1:03:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙有点东西要给你看看\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Simon has something he wanted to show you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.49,1:03:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 噢 钥匙 - 不 不行\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Oh. Key. - No, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.59,1:03:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 钥匙 - 不行\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Key. - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.99,1:03:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钥匙 我还要别的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Key. I have more.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.43,1:03:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.06,1:03:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去配多一把 省得以后麻烦\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'll get a copy cut. Save future confusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.86,1:03:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗯 这样就好 - 不 不 对不起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Well, this better be good. - Oh no, no, no, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.19,1:03:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯坦利 站起来 让你看看你做出的成绩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You need to step up, Stanley. I wanna see some real work from you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.73,1:03:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实际上 我还得点时间才能做完\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Actually, I'm working on something at the moment, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.76,1:03:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 一些我… - 不要曲解我对你仁慈和善良啊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Something that I... - Don't mistake my kindness for weakness.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.42,1:03:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 西蒙 我觉得詹姆斯有其他女友 - 是的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Simon, I think that James is seeing someone else.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.86,1:03:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他告诉我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And he told me that
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.54,1:03:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有时候会在房间用望远镜偷窥我的公寓\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you sometimes watch my apartment from a telescope in your room,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.86,1:03:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这事我不介意 真的没关系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which I'm fine with actually, I don't really mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.63,1:03:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一种奇怪的安慰方式 但是…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's kind of reassuring in a strange way, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.06,1:03:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去咖啡厅说吧？那里比较少人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Wanna go to the coffee room? It's a little public.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.66,1:03:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是发现他外面那女人是谁 这事会很有趣\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It could be interesting to find out who else he's seeing.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.60,1:03:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听他说过这事吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Are you hearing this?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.53,1:03:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那意味着 他没有约会你？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Does that mean he's not seeing you?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.60,1:03:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样 他甚至尝试隐藏它\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Not that he's even trying to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.76,1:03:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是一个好人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He's not a very good guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.89,1:03:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道 我一早就知道的 但是却被他这样愚弄\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Which I know and I always have known, but to be made a fool of by him?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.96,1:03:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等下 是被一个恶棍愚弄\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One second. By a villain.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.83,1:03:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我清楚他是… - 噢 不 这不是你的错\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- I knew what he was... - Oh no. It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.46,1:03:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而 他说了些 他有多了解我的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Then he'd say something about how he knew me,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.66,1:03:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说 我是孤独的一个人 因为他清楚那种感觉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that he could tell I was a lonely person, because he knew what it was like
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.89,1:04:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很孤独 很失落 很无形\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to be lonely and lost and invisible.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.89,1:04:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像是…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Like...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.99,1:04:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以把双手 一直穿过你一样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Like someone could just push their hand straight through you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.49,1:04:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你肯定不是很理解他\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I think you should definitely not see him.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.56,1:04:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他告诉我 他就像木偶奇遇记那样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He told me he felt like Pinocchio.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.66,1:04:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你读过木偶奇遇记吗？- 没有\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Do you know who Pinocchio is? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.63,1:04:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他像个小木偶人 被绳索牵制着\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He's this wooden boy. He's held up by strings.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.63,1:04:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他希望变成一个真人 你能理解吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He wants to feel like a real boy. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.63,1:04:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不能 - 我感觉就像木偶奇遇记\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- No. - I feel like Pinocchio.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.02,1:04:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.76,1:04:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以 今晚我能否到你公寓\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So is that okay if I come to your apartment tonight?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.63,1:04:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这样问有点奇怪 但我想亲自看看\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I know it's kinda strange to ask but I wanted to see for myself,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.86,1:04:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道他是否带女孩子回去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you know, if he's taking girls back there.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.76,1:04:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 抱歉 这不可能 因为我得工作\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, I'm sorry, that's not possible because I have to work.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.96,1:04:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 但是… - 我今晚不想回家 我想在这\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm not gonna be home tonight, I'll be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.16,1:04:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 你可以给我你家钥匙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But that's okay, you can just give me your key.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.19,1:04:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我没钥匙 - 你没钥匙？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- I don't have a key. - You don't have a key?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.59,1:04:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.42,1:04:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有你家里的钥匙？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You don't have a key to your own apartment?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.09,1:04:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 没有 - 那你怎么进屋？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- No. - How do you get in?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.66,1:04:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我进不去 - 你为什么撒谎？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- I can't get in. - Why are you lying?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.46,1:04:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没撒谎 我不知道…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm not. I just don't know...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.89,1:04:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,监视人是否是个好主意\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If it's a good idea to spy on people.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.09,1:04:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.16,1:04:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你可能会变得有点强迫症\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I think you might be becoming a little obsessive.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.59,1:04:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你为什么碰我？- 我没有\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Why are you touching me? - I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.43,1:04:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I just...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.46,1:04:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Also...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.02,1:05:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉像木偶奇遇记\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Feel like Pinocchio.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.62,1:05:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是个奸诈的小人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You're a snake.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.56,1:06:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可没做什么坏事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I haven't done anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.16,1:07:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.02,1:07:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是个宾客 我想要登记\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm a visitor. I would like to sign in.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.96,1:07:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.69,1:07:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫西蒙·詹姆斯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}My name is Simon James.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.12,1:07:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,员工服务室找你 西蒙·詹姆斯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You're wanted in worker services, Simon James.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.99,1:07:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.72,1:07:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.76,1:07:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不幸的小伙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mmm. Poor chap.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.09,1:07:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.49,1:08:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你不再存在了 - 什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- You don't exist any more. - Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.69,1:08:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 系统里你已不复存在了 - 那再把我录入系统\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- You're no longer on the system. - Well, just put me back in the system.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.82,1:08:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不能把你录入系统 - 为什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- I can't put you back in the system. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.43,1:08:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你不存在了 我不能把不存在的人录入系统\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Because you don't exist. I can't put someone who doesn't exist in the system.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.79,1:08:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我之前曾存在系统中啊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But I used to be in the system.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.16,1:08:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实际上 那不是我们这套系统了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Not according to the system. In fact,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.62,1:08:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根据我们系统显示 你从来不存在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}according to the system, you've never existed.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.82,1:08:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你们的系统可靠不？- 嘿 我们的系统十分可靠\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- How reliable is the system? - Hey, it's completely reliable.
