Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.92,1:13:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马丁 能让他出来一下吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Would you excuse us, please, Martin?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.86,1:13:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 詹姆斯先生 能和你说几句吗？- 好的 可以\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Mr. James, can I have a word? - Yeah, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.46,1:13:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还要在这一直…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'll just keep going with this...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.12,1:13:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照顾这个天杀的家伙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And take care of this bloody guy!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.96,1:13:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她之前试过这样做吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Has she tried anything like this before?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.66,1:13:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该没有\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.82,1:13:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你们经常吵架吗？- 有时候\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Do you fight a lot? - Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.09,1:13:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我恐怕她流产了 抱歉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm afraid to say she's had a miscarriage. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.79,1:13:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是她第一次怀孕吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Was it your first pregnancy?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.49,1:13:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是的 - 可喜的是 她身体没什么大碍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Yes. - The good thing is she's healthy
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.92,1:13:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胎儿还不大 所以她没承受多大的痛苦\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and it was very early, so she won't feel too much pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.56,1:13:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事已如此\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}These things happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.19,1:13:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也别怪责自己了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You mustn't blame yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.69,1:14:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可能会以为 我会感激你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You probably think I should be thankful
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.79,1:14:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感激你送我到医院 但我不会\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that you took me to the hospital, but I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.66,1:14:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想去死 而现在 我恐怕没勇气再去尝试一次\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I wanted to die and now I'm afraid I won't have the courage to try again.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.46,1:15:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我在想什么吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Do you wanna know what I think?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.69,1:15:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你也应该自杀\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I think that you should kill yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.62,1:15:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会中途阻止你的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I promise I won't try to stop you halfway through.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.79,1:17:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 嗯 这是给西蒙·詹姆斯…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hi, uh, this is a message for...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.82,1:17:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的留言\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Simon James.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.99,1:17:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃 你妈妈今天早上去世了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Uh, your mother passed away this morning
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.69,1:17:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是严重的脑…风\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}following a major ce-ree-bral
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.96,1:17:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脑部…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}s... ceree-bral?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.62,1:17:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中… 脑中风\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Cere-bral... Cerebral occurrence.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.66,1:17:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 按照她的遗愿 她会在今晚入葬\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Um, in accordance with her wishes, she's to be buried at night.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.99,1:17:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想要参加葬礼\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you wish to attend the funeral,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.49,1:17:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚半夜 葬礼会在墓地进行\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it starts at midnight at the cemetery
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.56,1:17:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,墓地在护理院的后面 不是后面 嗯…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to the rear of the home. Not the rear but, um...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.92,1:17:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,墓地在护理院后面 下面的那边直走就是了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To the... down the side and then towards the rear of the home.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.46,1:17:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 再见\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}All right. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.56,1:17:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽管我穿过死亡之谷…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yea, though I walk through the valley
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.66,1:17:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我也无所畏惧 因为你与我同在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of the shadow of death I will fear no evil for thou art with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.66,1:17:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你的杖 你的竿… - 现在别看\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Thy rod and thy staff... - Don't look now.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.19,1:17:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们都会安慰我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They will comfort me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.99,1:18:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为我准备筵席 你为我抵御敌人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thou preparest a table before me in the presence of mine enemies.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.92,1:18:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 我们都会帮助你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Look look, we can get you help,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.76,1:18:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是家庭哀悼时候 别来捣乱\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but now is a time for family. Just don't engage.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.76,1:18:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是谁？- 这人他妈是谁？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Who are you? Who is this fuck?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.49,1:18:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么和他长得一样？你们怎么都一个样？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Why have you got his face? Why have you got his face?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.19,1:18:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 别来捣乱 别捣乱 - 他是神经病？你神经病？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Just don't engage. Don't engage. - Is he mental? Are you mental?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.76,1:18:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 别来捣乱 - 你在干什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Just don't engage. - What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.19,1:18:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好了 - 别碰我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Okay. - Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.49,1:18:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 别捣乱 - 哟喔\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Don't engage. - Oi!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.99,1:18:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哟喔\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oi!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.66,1:18:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 别捣乱 - 别碰我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Don't engage. - Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.79,1:18:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.72,1:18:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Get up.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.19,1:18:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我站起来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Get off your knees.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.66,1:19:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.09,1:19:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你要去哪里？- 滚开\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Where are you going? - Fuck off!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.86,1:20:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 嘿 詹姆斯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh hey, James.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.89,1:20:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 噢 天啊 看看你 - 你知道我是谁 对吧？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Oh my God, look at you. - You know who I am, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.19,1:20:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你还好吗？- 你认得出我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Are you okay? - You recognize me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.02,1:20:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 西蒙 发生什么事了？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Of course. Simon, what happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.72,1:20:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想变成一个被绳索操控的傀儡\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I don't want to be a boy held up by string.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.82,1:20:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好的 - 好了？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Okay. - Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.82,1:20:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.46,1:21:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.89,1:21:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.16,1:22:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在我所在的位置\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That is where I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.56,1:22:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我现在看着他\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yes, I am looking at him now.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.66,1:22:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他好像想要跳下去了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He is about to jump.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.82,1:22:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请赶快\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Please hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.49,1:25:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这样的人很少有啊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There aren't too many like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.69,1:25:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是 西蒙？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Are there, Simon?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.89,1:26:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我是唯一的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'd like to think I'm pretty unique.

